<%- include('partials/header', {title: 'Deposit Policy | Shanti & Bryan Pinscher Kennel'}) %>

<section class="page-section">
  <p class="section-label">Our Reservation Policy</p>
  <h1>Do We Require a Deposit?</h1>
  <div class="section-underline"></div>

  <div class="deposit-answer">
    <p class="deposit-yes"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> Yes, a deposit is required to reserve a puppy.</p>
    <p style="color:var(--text-light);max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;">A deposit secures your chosen puppy and reserves it exclusively for you. Once a deposit is placed, the puppy is marked as <strong>Reserved</strong> and is no longer available to other buyers.</p>
  </div>

  <h2 style="margin-top:60px;">Why We Ask for a Deposit</h2>
  <div class="section-underline"></div>

  <div class="deposit-grid">
    <div class="deposit-card">
      <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-lock"></i></div>
      <h3>It Secures Your Puppy</h3>
      <p>A deposit holds your chosen puppy exclusively for you, so no one else can reserve it while you prepare for your new family member.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="deposit-card">
      <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-handshake"></i></div>
      <h3>It Shows Serious Commitment</h3>
      <p>Deposits help ensure our puppies go to genuinely committed homes, allowing us to plan responsibly for each puppy's future.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="deposit-card">
      <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-heart-pulse"></i></div>
      <h3>It Supports Their Care</h3>
      <p>Deposits contribute toward the continued veterinary care, vaccinations, and quality nutrition your puppy receives before going home.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="deposit-card">
      <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-check"></i></div>
      <h3>It Confirms the Timeline</h3>
      <p>A reservation lets us coordinate pick-up or delivery dates with confidence and keep you updated every step of the way.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="deposit-note">
    <p><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info" style="color:var(--gold);margin-right:8px;"></i> The deposit is applied toward the total price of your puppy. To discuss reserving a puppy or for details about our deposit amount, please reach out through our contact page.</p>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-top:36px;">
    <a href="/contact" class="btn">Reserve a Puppy</a>
    <a href="/puppies" class="btn btn-gold" style="margin-left:12px;">View Available Puppies</a>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>